<TEXT>
<P>
 Nicole Erickson has been named State girls' basketball player of the year by 
Cal-Hi Sports. In her four years at Brea-Olinda, Erickson was the point guard 
for teams that finished a combined 130-5 and won four consecutive State 
championships. 
</P>
<P>
