Huntington Beach's Tony Gonzalez was a second-team selection, and Santa Ana 
Valley's Olujimi Mann and Mater Dei's Schea Cotton made the sixth team. Mann 
was named sophomore player of the year and Cotton freshman of the year. 
</P>
