<HEADLINE>
<P>
ORANGE COUNTY FOCUS: BUENA PARK; DISTRICT FAIR OPEN TO TEACHING APPLICANTS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By DEBRA CANO 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Teachers looking for a job are invited to attend Centralia School District's 
recruitment fair Saturday.The recruitment fair will be from 9 to 11 a.m. at the 
district office, 6625 La Palma Ave. 
</P>
<P>
 The district is looking for regular and bilingual teachers as well as resource 
specialists. The district also is interested in people pursuing a teaching 
career in kindergarten through sixth grade. The district has nine elementary 
schools in Buena Park, Anaheim and La Palma. 
</P>
<P>
 Those attending can learn about the district, meet and talk with principals 
and ask questions. Applicants will be able to sign up for a future interview. 
</P>
<P>
 For information or reservations: (714) 228-3179.DEBRA CANO 
