E. Broadway. 
</P>
<P>
 The festival runs from 11 a.m. to 5 p.m. and will be held at the Koll Anaheim 
Center, at West Harbor Place and Anaheim Boulevard. 
</P>
<P>
 The event is sponsored by the Leo Freedman Foundation in cooperation with the 
Anaheim Arts Council, the city of Anaheim and the Anaheim Museum. 
</P>
<P>
 For more information or to reserve free symphony tickets, call (714) 778-3301. 
