million, or 84 cents a share, compared to year-ago earnings of $243 million, or 
80 cents. The most recent quarter includes a charge of $120 million, or 26 
cents a share, for damages to be paid to Stac Electronics stemming from a 
patent infringement lawsuit. Excluding the charge, Microsoft said net income 
would have been $336 million, or $1.11 a share. 
