<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA041994-0172 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 033685 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
April 19, 1994, Tuesday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Business; Part D; Page 4; Column 1; Financial Desk 
</P>
