 South: Irvine Spectrum area, San Clemente, San Juan Capistrano, Aliso Viejo, 
Dana Point, Laguna Hills, Laguna Niguel, Mission Viejo, Foothill Ranch, El 
Toro, Rancho Santa Margarita 
</P>
<P>
