<P>
 Manu, 54, owner of a small print shop 
</P>
<P>
 Minnie, 44, partner in the shop 
</P>
<P>
 Leila and Pravina, both 19, students 
</P>
<P>
 Sarita, 6, student 
</P>
<P>
 * 
</P>
