</P>
<P>
 * 
</P>
<P>
 Louis Botha: "White South Africans, Afrikaans- or English-speaking, are 
extremely unsure .... about the future.... My philosophy has been to stockpile 
the guns and ammunition that I would need to defend my family if we were 
attacked, but to work for a better future for all." 
</P>
