<HEADLINE>
<P>
MYSTERY WOMAN RESTORES FAITH 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 * My faith in the human race has been validated because on April 7 I left my 
purse in a cart at Home Depot, Glendale.I returned there shortly after but 
found no purse. Within an hour a woman returned the purse to my husband at his 
office with everything in it completely intact. She left no name or phone 
number and told my husband she was in a hurry.  
</P>
<P>
 So the only way I can convey my deep gratitude and thanks, to let her know how 
much I really appreciate her honesty, is in this newspaper, hoping that somehow 
she'll see this. 
</P>
<P>
 Thank you again, mystery woman, whoever you are. 
</P>
<P>
 GLORIA RUFFALO 
</P>
<P>
 Glendale 
</P>
