Kennedy Coach Sue Hall said Pitt is more dominating than ever. She opened the 
week by pitching consecutive no-hitters, beating Rancho Alamitos, 1-0, Tuesday 
and Bolsa Grande, 3-0, Thursday. She then pitched a three-hit shutout in a 1-0 
victory over Garden Grove that kept the Fighting Irish alone in first place. 
Pitt improved her record to 11-1 and lowered her ERA to 0.30. Other notables: 
